{
  "text": "We downloaded the Atlantic salmon Expressed Sequence Tags (ESTs) from National Center for Biotechnology Information (NCBI) and extracted the 3\u2032 UTR sequences. miRNA target prediction was performed using Miranda [CITATION_1] with strict seed match, free energy < \u2212 20 kcal/mol, and the pairing score > 150.",
